      "title": "Sri Lanka shares up in mid-day trade",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "ECONOMYNEXT \u2013 Sri Lanka\u2019s shares gained in mid-morning trade on July 18 with liquid index moving up over 1 percent, Colombo Stock Exchange d ata showed.",
        "The main All Share Price Index up 0.93 percent or 69.72 points to 7,537.54 at 1140 hours.",
        "The most liquid S&P SL20 up 1.29 percent or 30.85 points to 2,431."
